  "Description": {
    "English": "A highly refined food product, created in the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span>.<br><br>These cake-like nutrients are processed from a base of <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Extra-Fluffy Batter</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>生成的高度精炼食品。<br><br>这些蛋糕状营养素使用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">超蓬松面糊</span>加工而成。",
    "TencentChinese": "通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>生成的高度精炼食品。<br><br>这些蛋糕状营养素使用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">超蓬松面糊</span>加工而成。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種高度精製的食用產品，是在<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器</span>中製成。<br><br>如蛋糕一般的營養素，用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">超蓬鬆麵糊</span>為基底加工而成。"
  },
